  "notes": "Product relationship roots replayable parity scenario captured against a disposable Shopify dev-store setup. The parity runner seeds the captured products, collection, and product media, then executes collection, option, and variant-media relationship roots through the local proxy and compares mutation payloads plus downstream read-after-write effects with strict JSON targets. Selling-plan product/variant association roots from the same capture are enforced by the dedicated selling-plan-product-variant-associations scenario."
